name: Pipedream (1)
description:
"Pipedreams" is a series of abstract forms varying in shape, space, and material - inspired by relationships found within nature and technology. "Pipedream (1)" is the first of this series that I am releasing as a giveaway to say thank you to everyone who has purchased and supported my artwork. 

Sculpted and rendered in Blender.
4320 × 5280px.
